    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2192635/" class="title-link">了解中国共产党早期历史的一部重要文献</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2192635"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2725178/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2725178-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2725178/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">旺旺</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-04"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-04 00:13:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2192635_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  对中国共产党早期历史的一项学术探究，据说是西方本研究领域的开山之作，是史华慈的博士论文基础上修改而成。现在看来恐怕并没有多少独到的见解，或者说很多独到的见解已经被大家接受了。他用简短的篇幅向世人展示了刚刚崛起的中国共产主义，对于其如何发生、如何发展、如何跃...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2192635_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2192635_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
